1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:16,340
Begin with accounts, group membership, and every component of the target path. Alice and Bob belong to webteam; outsider does not. The existing owner and modes explain why collaboration currently fails.

2
00:00:16,690 --> 00:00:28,110
chown assigns the share to webteam. Mode 2770 grants owner and group access, blocks others, and sets setgid so new files inherit the directory group. The existing checklist receives mode 660.

3
00:00:28,460 --> 00:00:40,760
Real operations as Alice and Bob prove the positive cases. A separate write test as outsider must fail; otherwise the design is not least privilege.

4
00:00:41,110 --> 00:00:50,210
The final stat output proves numeric modes, group ownership, and inherited webteam membership on Alice's new file. The checklist content proves Bob performed a genuine group write.
